wikipedia_page.main: Catherine Mary Mowat (born 20 September 1952) is an English former cricketer who played as a right-arm medium bowler. She appeared in 5 Test matches and 3 One Day Internationals for England between 1978 and 1984. She played domestic cricket for Middlesex.
